About this item

  • CompatibilityOnly designed for iPhone 16 Pro Max 6.9 inch.
  • Pioneer 100% Privacy ProtectionUGREEN iPhone 16 Pro Max privacy screen protector offers an ultra-narrow 28 privacy angle, providing a broad 152 anti spy range, which means the screen can only seen by the person facing it. Effectively protect your privacy and important information from strangers and outlookers on metro, elevator, bank, office and any other public occasions.
  • TOP 9H+ Glass, Ultimate Drop DefenseAdopting upgraded Military-Grade composite anti-drop tempered glass with 2024 debuting anti-compress edge technology, UGREEN 16 Pro Max Screen Protector has a hardness level far exceeding 9H and can effectively resist against the most common edge cracking situations without fear of any drop or impact.
  • Seamless Fit, 1:1 Full CoverageUsing iPhone 16 Pro Max to make 1:1 screen shape replication, UGREEN private screen protector encircles every curve of the screen with a strengthened black edge, completely protecting the vulnerable screen edges from cracking and preventing dust from sticking to the edges.
  • Easy to InstallJust use the alignment frame and finish the film application in 1 minute! The package also comes with two sets of dust-repellent adhesive and cleaning kit, which can ensure effortless, bubble-free application.
  • Professional & Strict R&D SystemUGREEN is committed to creating professional phone cases and screen protectors that can lead the industry standards. The most recent technologies are continuously being developed by our experimental R&D department, and our products must go through 12 rigorous quality inspection tests before reaching customers' hands.
  • What You Get2 * UGREEN privacy screen protector for iPhone 16 Pro Max, 1* alignment frame, 2* installation accessory kit, 1 * user manual, 24-month warranty, 24-hour customer service, lifetime technical support.

How are ratings calculated?
To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyses reviews to verify trustworthiness.
